MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-2509. Thompson v. Utomo.

Lucas County, No. L-95-034. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Lucas County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective April 9,1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
